21
00:01:05,190 --> 00:01:07,560
[in Hangul]
From what I heard, the medical officer

22
00:01:07,650 --> 00:01:09,770
is going to check for people who smoke.

23
00:01:13,740 --> 00:01:15,360
Take a look at my basket.

24
00:01:18,110 --> 00:01:19,740
[all] Ooh…

25
00:01:19,820 --> 00:01:21,530
