What do you say? Deal?

28
00:01:27,370 --> 00:01:29,460
[all] Deal! Deal! Deal!

29
00:01:29,540 --> 00:01:30,630
-[soldier 2] Spray me!
-[soldier 3] Hurry up!

30
00:01:30,710 --> 00:01:33,840
