31
00:01:35,300 --> 00:01:37,340
[soldier 2]
The military police knows what we need.

32
00:01:38,970 --> 00:01:40,300
[soldier 3] Come on, spray me.

33
00:01:40,390 --> 00:01:41,930
[soldier 4] Spray me next.

34
00:01:42,010 --> 00:01:44,810
[soldier 3]
What would we have done without him?

35
00:01:47,520 --> 00:01:48,770
[personnel] Officer Han.

36
00:01:49,940 --> 00:01:51,230
Officer Han.

37
00:01:55,240 --> 00:01:56,110
Me?

38
00:01:56,690 --> 00:01:59,160
[personnel] Pack your things.
The medical officer wants you out.

39
00:02:00,570 --> 00:02:01,620
Already?

40
00:02:01,700 --> 00:02:04,040
He says you're fine
and wants you back at your unit.

41
00:02:04,580 --> 00:02:05,540
Gosh.

42
00:02:06,160 --> 00:02:08,160
