43
00:02:12,380 --> 00:02:13,670
Let's all leave together.

44
00:02:14,710 --> 00:02:16,300
They've all been smoking.

45
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:20,510
[theme music plays]

46
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:44,870
♪ Since I've been dreaming for too long ♪

47
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:52,290
♪ I can't find the reasons to move on ♪

48
00:02:55,380 --> 00:02:57,760
♪ Wake up to reality ♪

49
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:01,300
♪ Realize we're getting old ♪

50
